price: (Innis) ni jedhe: “Waan Gooftaan kiyya isa keessatti naaf mijeessetu caala. humnaan na gargaaraa, Gidduu keessaniifi isaaniitti cufaa nan godhaa, .
arabic: قَالَ مَا مَكَّنِّي فِيهِ رَبِّي خَيۡرٞ فَأَعِينُونِي بِقُوَّةٍ أَجۡعَلۡ بَيۡنَكُمۡ وَبَيۡنَهُمۡ رَدۡمًا

version.title: Oromo translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Oromo by Ghaly Ababour Abaghuna, printed in 2009.
